- momentloop-receiver folder is a ReactNative/Expo app to display photos and videos sent by momentloop-sender
- momentloop-sender folder is another ReactNative/Expo app to send photos and videos to the receiver
- server folder is a Deno/Fastify server to process video, convert them and then sent push notif to the receiver
- poc folder contains a list of POC for React Native / Expo
- use jest for tests
- use just over bash scripts